Nollywood actress, Nkechi Blessing Sunday is full of thanks after a stranger/fan sent N1million to her account after she made a live video begging fans for money. The excited actress took to instagram to share the news, while beckoning on the anonymous sender to reveal himself so she would thank him specially. In her words; “I was on live video earlier begging my fans for money, pinned my acct details and den boom someone sent me 1 million naira😳😳😳 I am still shocked ooo😳😳 dear sender pls kindly DM me let me thank you specially 😳😳 to those that sent 1k and the likes God bless you all abundantly 🙏🏻 I am still in shock😳 1m just like that? Haa” Source